
Code for the BEST (Bayesian Estimation Supersedes t-Test) package based on John Kruschke's program, which is available at \url{http://www.indiana.edu/~kruschke/BEST/}.

It implements the method of Kruschke (2012) Bayesian estimation supersedes the t test. \emph{Journal of Experimental Psychology: General}, First Posting. doi: 10.1037/a0029146.

For more on the approach used, see the book: Kruschke (2011) \emph{Doing Bayesian data analysis: a tutorial with R and BUGS}. Elsevier, Amsterdam etc.

